          "_name": "article21",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article021\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"reverseContent\" title=\"Reverse\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showButton\" title=\"Buttons\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card Color\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" name=\"iconColor\" value=\"#9fe870\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#edefeb\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n                    <h5 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                        Meine Qualifikationen:<b>&nbsp;</b></h5>\n                    <h6 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle, .main-button\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"></h6>\n                    <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-3  main-button\" mbr-if=\"showButton\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                        <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                            Learn more\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-lg-8 side-features\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-left\">\n                    <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                        <ul>\n                            <li>2021/22: Ausbildung zur Stillberaterin bei der La Leche Liga&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>2025: Fortbildung \"Grundlagen zur Ernährung mit Anfangs(milch)nahrungen\" beim FeS-Institut</li>\n                            <li>2025/26: Ausbildung zur ganzheitlichen Baby- und Kinderschlafberaterin beim Verein Kinderschlaf</li>\n                            <li>2026: Fortbildung \"Wenn Geburt zum Trauma wird\" bei Ute Taschner</li>\n                            <li>seit 2026: Ausbildung zur Stillassistentin bei e-learning Stillberatung (die für die Anmeldung zur IBCLC-Prüfung nötigen 95 Stunden laktationsspezifische Fortbildung sind darin enthalten)</li>\n                            <li>Kontinuierliche Weiterbildung durch den regelmäßigen Besuch von Regionaltreffen und Jahreskonferenzen der La Leche Liga.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</b></li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
